an></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4anyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=150c0036\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4anyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=8aa5942d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"3f46f8bc6c22df44b6a350150a165161c4220aaa","tid":1678293,"uid":83,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4bb0804f718ab398a97335846155b5b6ec814980","tid":1678293,"uid":5569,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e5f9419f07ab4c497e32e160988a4863b2e4c377","tid":1678293,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"18區仲有咩區未unlock"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"青衣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"十八區：<br />